{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":84426,"known_for_department":"Writing","name":"Olivier Nakache","original_name":"Olivier Nakache","popularity":0.4698,"profile_path":"/cLfpk5eIT8h7NnZcz6Iti3DPkRu.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/cK070s3Qdn1Ib7Gq8RgIyJKgvu3.jpg","id":77338,"title":"The Intouchables","original_title":"Intouchables","overview":"A true story of two men who should never have met – a quadriplegic aristocrat who was injured in a paragliding accident and a young man from the projects.","poster_path":"/1QU7HKgsQbGpzsJbJK4pAVQV9F5.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"fr","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":22.7985,"release_date":"2011-11-02","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.271,"vote_count":18445},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/10ECHyeW7vZMjCLSRLak9K5fVdB.jpg","id":432068,"title":"C'est la vie!","original_title":"Le Sens de la fête","overview":"Max is a battle-weary veteran of the wedding-planning racket. His latest — and last — gig is a hell of a fête, involving stuffy period costumes for the caterers, a vain, hyper- sensitive singer who thinks he's a Gallic James Brown, and a morose, micromanaging groom determined to make Max's night as miserable as possible. But what makes the affair too bitter to endure is that Max's colleague and ostensible girlfriend, Joisette, seems to have written him off, coolly going about her professional duties while openly flirting with a much younger server. It's going to be a very long night… especially once the groom's aerial serenade gets underway.","poster_path":"/e9hIxAKPdXo9Fgwca6vT4USOXK6.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"fr","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":2.0745,"release_date":"2017-10-04","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.022,"vote_count":1609},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ct2I74zKDrK1Ts2jJa9WixJrigg.jpg","id":440472,"title":"The Upside","original_title":"The Upside","overview":"Phillip is a wealthy quadriplegic who needs a careta